## 3. Rules and docs — unqualified log paths

| Location | Issue | Action |
|----------|--------|--------|
| **.cursor/rules/always/mcp-obsidian-integration.mdc** | "Append to … Ingest-Log.md" (no path). | Use "3-Resources/Ingest-Log.md" (and specify 3-Resources path for mcp-setup-log if kept). |
| **.cursor/sync/rules/always/mcp-obsidian-integration.md** | Same. | Sync after rule change. |
| **.cursor/sync/rules/context/para-zettel-autopilot.md** | "Log … in Ingest-Log.md", "Log … into both Ingest-Log.md and 3-Resources/Backup-Log.md". | Use "3-Resources/Ingest-Log.md" for consistency. |
| **3-Resources/Cursor-Project-Rules-Summary.md** | "mcp-setup-log.md or Ingest-Log.md". | Use "3-Resources/Ingest-Log.md"; clarify mcp-setup-log location if kept. |
| **3-Resources/2026-02-23-obsidian-log-action.md** | "default Ingest-Log.md". | State that default is root-relative and pipelines should pass `3-Resources/Ingest-Log.md` (or correct per-pipeline path). |
| **3-Resources/Autonomous-Runs-Options-Reference.md** | log_path example "Ingest-Log.md". | Use "3-Resources/Ingest-Log.md" in examples. |
| **Second-Brain-Starter-Kit** (rules, README, Troubleshooting, Session-Prep, QuickAdd) | Multiple "Ingest-Log.md" refs. | Point all to `3-Resources/Ingest-Log.md` in Starter-Kit. |

