## 7. Scripts and folders

| Item | Current / canonical | Deprecated / vestigial | Action |
|------|---------------------|------------------------|--------|
| **Logging/** | Not in Vault-Layout or Logs.md as a standard folder. | Contains `clone-and-install-mcp.js` writing to `mcp-setup-log.md` at vault root. Starter-Kit plan says "do not include … Logging/". | Treat as optional/setup-only. Either move script (and log) under 3-Resources and document, or mark as legacy "one-off MCP setup" and leave out of main layout. |
| **mcp-server/** | MCP typically runs from Cursor global config (~/.cursor/mcp.json), not vault-local clone. | clone-and-install-mcp.js clones into `mcp-server/`. | If no longer used, document as legacy or remove; otherwise document as optional local clone path. |

